sub_title: Full-stack Web Developer / Node.js / Express / React / Vue.js / Sequelize
summary:
I began with my first steps as a web developer in 2012 when I developed a website for a company I created in Argentina. After that, I started focusing on Digital Marketing because it was what my company required. In 2017 I decided to move forwards and I sold the company, then I create a tiny company and started developing websites with WordPress mainly. From there my curiosity about web development grew and in 2020 I started learning Javascript in particular. Along my learning path, I followed Freecodecamp.org Front End Web Development course.
At the present I'm developing a cross-device plants marketplace with Vue.js and Ionic, it will be released soon.

Check my Github repos: https://github.com/jmaguero/
My website: https://jmaguero.github.io/
